            <h1 id="whats-new">What’s new?</h1>

<div class="va-introtext">
  The latest news and updates on the Design System, Forms library and the Content style guide.
</div>

<va-alert close-btn-aria-label="Close notification" status="warning" visible="" uswds="">
  <h2 slot="headline">
    v1 components have now been deprecated
  </h2>
  <div>
    <p classname="vads-u-margin-y--0">
      If your team is still using a v1 component, instances will be flagged in the Collab Cycle and may be considered launch blocking. <a href="/about/developers/using-web-components#uswds-v1-to-v3-migration">Learn how to migrate a component</a>.
    </p>
  </div>
</va-alert>

<h2 id="summer-2024">Summer 2024</h2>

<p>The team synced up typography with USWDS v3 and continues to focus on syncing up iconography and replacing v1 components with their v3 equivalents.</p>

