  <li>va-header-minimal: add optional headings (#1084)</li>
  <li>updated CSS-Library version in web-components (#1086)</li>
  <li>va-text-input and va-textarea error message not announced by screen readers (#2572)</li>
  <li>Updated all instances of color-primary-darker and color-primary-darkest in vets-website#2311</li>
</ul>

